title: first post. who's rectifier00x?
description: the beginning. who i am. what this site is. what's coming.
content:
yo.

i finally made this thing. been thinking about it for a while. Now it's real

a little introduction.

I'm rectifier00x.that's what you can call me. but my real name is David.

i can describe myself as an internet generalist (whatever that means)

i built this site because i needed a place that's mine. somewhere to dump all the stuff i find (digital ones). music, docs, software, books, audiobooks, all other good stuff. Especial those hidden from cooperate internet.

i'll also be yapping here a lot .sharing my thoughts .random stuff.whatever i feel like writing about.

A heads up ,i'm not an expert on anything ,that's to mean that anything i share here i just but my oponions and findings of some guy who spends too much of his online .


so what's that plan?

the plan is to post often .daily if i can .let's see if i actually stick to it. (future me i hope you are happy right now)


anyway first post done . felt weird writing this but here it is. it's a short intro but future post will be longer .i will leave you with a quote for today



Simplicity is the principle of art.

--Bruce lee
